data.chText: 有才能的；天才的；有才干的
data.enText: having a natural ability to do sth well

value.def: Someone who is talented has a natural ability to do something well.

example.tran: 霍华德是个很有天分的钢琴家。

example.ex: She has a huge army of young fans, and is extremely talented.
example.tran: 她拥有一大批年轻的崇拜者，而且她极具天赋。

trans: 人才；有才能的人；全方面发展的人才；人才优势
